c: 7
v: 53
t: "Are they only waiting for it to be interpreted? The day its interpretation comes along, those who have already forgotten it will say: \"Our Lord´s messengers did bring the Truth! Have we any intercessors to intercede for us? Or should we be sent back, then we would act so differently from the way we have been acting.\" They have lost their souls and what they have been inventing has left them in the lurch"